ng config cli.packageManager yarn

Make sure your app.module.ts doesn't already have akita things imported...
If it does then remove the akita imports, the environment import and the akita devtools line from the module imports array

and then...

ng add @datorama/akita
  ? Set up Akita's devtools? Yes
  ? Set up Akita's router store? No

ng g component orders
ng g component orders/order
ng g component orders/menu
ng g component orders/menu/menu-item

ng g component locations/location

ng g feature menu-item --dirName=state/menu-item
ng g feature locations --dirName=state/locations

> copy the locations and menu-items json assets from https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/tree/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/assets

> copy file from https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/state/api-response.ts

> fill out the menu-item model (id, name, price)
  should look like: https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/state/menu-items/menu-item.model.ts

> fill out location models (id, name, address, phone)
  should look like: https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/state/locations/location.model.ts

> update services to request the proper .json assets
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/state/menu-items/menu-items.service.ts
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/state/locations/locations.service.ts

> update location component to have an Input() Location and render it
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/locations/location/location.component.ts
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/locations/location/location.component.html

> inject locations query into locations component and render locations using the location component (add location search feature?)
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/locations/locations.component.ts
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/locations/locations.component.html

> update menu-item component to have an Input() MenuItem and render it
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/orders/menu/menu-item/menu-item.component.ts
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/orders/menu/menu-item/menu-item.component.html

> inject menu-item query into menu component and render items using the menu-item component (add item search feature?)
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/orders/menu/menu.component.ts
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/orders/menu/menu.component.html

> update orders component template to render menu items and order
  https://github.com/unos-it/teach-outs/blob/step2/ProjectBobs/Bobs/src/app/orders/orders.component.html

ng serve -o

Hopefully you have a working app?
